[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm contemplating whether to use Docker directly, which avoids extra Maven dependencies, or to include Testcontainers, which requires additional dependencies and images. The Neo4j driver might be applied before generation, but it seems unnecessary to add Testcontainers to our scaffold due to added metadata demands. Since the user explicitly requested not to apply setup, I need to choose an image wisely. I'll use the current LTS version 5.26.27 for compatibility, as DBMS 5.28 isn’t suitable.
[thinking] 
